short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Reading Thai political news from a different perspective

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: To open up the mind of Thais, seeing the political situation with a different perspective is crucial. Trayut will encourage Thai users to consider far beyond "WHO" into "WHAT" the politician do to our society.
